content.text:
I'm ready to help you with your VibeLife project! I can see this is a fortune-telling and relationship analysis application with both API (Python/FastAPI) and web (Next.js) components.

Based on the git status, I can see you have:
- Various modified files across the API and web apps
- Some archived/deleted files (mirror, reminders, fortune components)
- New test files and features (bazi, zodiac, interview sessions)
- Configuration updates and deployment files

What would you like me to help you with? I can:
- Run tests or build commands
- Review or modify code
- Help with git operations
- Execute any other bash commands you need
Just let me know what you'd like to do!
